name: Brain Zaps VII
description:
This piece is part of a series of mine (Chaotic Mind , 2022).

-

"The wind was howling and the rain was pouring down in a dark night. I was walking through the forest, when I saw a rabbit running away. I followed it, but I soon lost track of it. I was getting really confused. I didn't know where I was or what I was doing. Suddenly, I saw a light in the distance. I approached it and saw a beautiful palace. The door was open and I walked inside. I was in a mental confusion."

-

Abstract light-painting created with steel wool on fire in pitch darkness. It was complemented by digital art. 

*

'Brain Zaps VII', 2022
